message.body: Hello there
Got a question?
Do you like the study?
Or just unsure of the procedure?
It seems pretty simple. The procedure that is.
I don't really have an opinion on it.
It hasn't interfered w anything
But if I win some money that will sway me
Had a few cool chats too; some interesting people involved
U live in Philly?
Not anymore; live an hour north of Philly
U? Are u a student, graduate, prof?
Graduate. U?
Finished my phd last year
Cool congrats. What's next?
Thanks! Doing my postdoc and studying for licensure (clinical psych). How about u?
Director of biz development for marketing company
Very cool! Been doing that long?
Do this company just about a year.
Is that what u want to do or are you working towards another position?
Having my own business is the ultimate goal.
Been involved in VC and start ups most of my career
I see and am right there with you! Building my business now, involved in one start-up and potentially partnering in another. So much more exciting than picking a place to be an employee forever!!
Very cool. Related to psychology?
Ultimately I want to have a wellness center and consulting to implement the same in corporate
So yeah, in a way.

I specialized in treating the most severe cases, so that there is almost nothing that I haven't seen clinically. But now I'm also enrolled in a school for integrative health so I can address all areas of wellness
Never imagined this would evolve so much
